FBIS3-18195 "drweu039_j_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Foreign Ministry: Israel Must Prevent Further Violence LD2502163594 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1529 GMT 25 Feb 94 LD2502163594 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Language: Italian Article Type:BFN [Text] "We expect the Israeli Government to adopt all necessary measures to prevent further bloodshed." This was stated by the Foreign Ministry, which added that "increased vigilance and a heightened sense of responsibility" are necessary following the Hebron massacre. A statement from the Foreign Ministry stresses that "we must make sure extremist fanaticism does not jeopardize the progress made toward peace." The statement further says that acts of "extremists on all sides" against normally defenseless citizens are aimed at dashing the hopes for peace.
